title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-10-2013 TUES
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-10-2013 TUES




Tuesday, December 10, 2013
Gay Wedding Cake Ruling

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. Hypocrisy of Obama administration in lack of prosecutions 
       against wind energy companies for killing bald eagles while 
          going after oil companies and utility companies. 

2. Court rules against bakery which refused to sell a wedding cake to a gay couple for religious reasons.



 - 10AM hour

Guest: David Hogberg, National Center for Public Policy Research 
                               Flawed report on ObamaCare by Families USA




 - 11AM hour

1. Mikes deconstruction of an attack on Walmart. 
2. Revisiting gay wedding cake court decision.
